<![CDATA[<div><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</span></div><div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b><br></b></span></font></div><div><span id="docs-internal-guid-7b385c20-384c-1f3d-4872-e53b104c8d80"><font size="2"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">We hope you are looking forward to starting your role on the autumn programme. </span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">At the end of the summer programme we process P45s for all staff - this concludes your employment with us. As we have processed your P45 you will need to submit a new tax declaration outlining your current circumstances. </span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">What are the next steps? </span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">You will need to respond to this email confirming in writing what your current situation is. The statement should represent your circumstances as they will be on the day you commence work with us. </span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Please use the following sentence as the body of the email</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The tax declaration statement which applies to my present circumstances is STATEMENT [insert statement letter A/B/C]. </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">NAME: [Insert name]</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">DATE: [insert date]</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">What are the tax declarations? </span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Your tax declaration can be </span><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">one of the following options</span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">:</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">A </span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">- This is my first job since last 6 April and I </span><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">have not </span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">been receiving taxable Jobseeker’s Allowance or taxable Incapacity Benefit or a state or occupational pension.</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">B </span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">- This is now my only job, but since last 6 April I </span><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">have </span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">had another job, or have received taxable Jobseeker’s Allowance or Incapacity Benefit. I do not receive a state or occupational pension.</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">C</span><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> - I have another job or receive a state or occupation pension.</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">When do I need to do this by? </span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3;margin-top:4pt;margin-bottom:8pt;margin-left: 2pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">You will need to send an email back by no later than 31st October. If you do not respond to this email you will be put on a tax code specifically for people whose current circumstances are unknown - which could mean you are taxed more than you should be. &nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3;margin-top:4pt;margin-bottom:8pt;margin-left: 2pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">More information on tax can be found on </span><a href="https://www.gov.uk/tax-codes/letters-in-your-tax-code-what-they-mean" style="text-decoration:none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(17, 85, 204); text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">HMRC or GOV.UK</span></a><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> website. </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3;margin-top:4pt;margin-bottom:8pt;margin-left: 2pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">If you have any questions please email us back. </span></p><div><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></div></font></span></div><div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b><br></b></span></font></div><div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Best wishes,</span></font></div><div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b><br></b></span></font></div><div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">NCS with The Challenge</span></font></div><div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">CCR 22b</span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div>]]></td>
